efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n * minSize)
space complexity: O(n)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Sliding-window counting of unique letters for every substring length from minSize up to maxSize; once any length yields a valid substring we can stop early because shorter substrings always dominate frequency.

